snippet.title: Bowman VS Zombies - Trailer
snippet.description:
Buy Bowman VS Zombies on Steam – https://store.steampowered.com/app/870740

Welcome to the world of BowmanVSZombies! 

BowmanVSZombies is a 3D and wave based video game. You play as a bowman and you need to survive to different waves of zombies in different levels!

For more information on BowmanVSZombies, follow these channels: 

Twitter – https://twitter.com/BowmanVSZombies
Website – https://bowmanvszombies.fr/
Facebook –https://www.facebook.com/bowmanvszombies/
